            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>For another, fragmentary, copy at Apollonia, see <ref type="inscription">A04600</ref>, and, for the fullest text, at Ptolemais, <ref type="inscription">P42400</ref></p>
            <p>It is clear that there was a considerable military force at Teucheira in the time of Anastasius
                    and possible that the Late Fort was originally constructed for it.</p>
